data.title: Nuclear Rabbit Lyrics, Meaning & Videos
data.meta_description: Lyrics to Nuclear Rabbit Secretly Meaty: I want some service asshole. I've been waiting here a half an hour. Some say your foods disturbing. Will I regret what I
data.text: The lyrics to Nuclear Rabbit's Secretly Meaty present a disgruntled customer seeking service at a restaurant. The singer is frustrated with the wait time and is hesitant to order from the menu, unsure if they will regret their decision. They address the server, Linda, with a confrontational attitude, referring to her as a "pea-brain napkin Maid" who needs to smile. Despite their reservations, the singer decides to order a slice of cow, or "forgotten beef," and receives a set of silverware with their meal. The song also mentions a character named Dirty Mike who enjoys the food at the restaurant and requests a plate of fries.
